  "body": "Currently it is possible to change screen orientation in Android app. In some cases, changing screen orientation to landscape mode results in broken layout, as can be seen on attached video. \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/160125720-96fde5db-a793-4a3c-954e-e85492ce0276.mp4\r\n\r\nIt would be better to disable changing of screen orientation to prevent from bugs connected to changing to landscape mode.\r\n \r\nIn case of IOS, changing of screen orientation is already disabled, so let's implement it for Android either. ",
